      "content": "I'm not really following the goblin analogies. Why are you using those? I just need to understand the actual cellular mechanisms for my exam. Can you explain the specific role of cytokines and chemokines in recruiting neutrophils versus how antigen presentation triggers the lymphocyte response? Please keep it professional.",
